On September 12th, the church released the second batch of new hymns. This page covers period between when the second batch came out and when the third batch will come out, whenever that will be. This page will update regularly as I collect more data. Currently I have data from 2,007 sacrament meetings between June 2nd and September 8th from 317 wards. 

